query:
UPDATE provider_offers
            SET
                provider_name = $2,
                price_kwh_electricity = $3,
                price_kwh_gas = $4,
                fixed_monthly_fee = $5,
                green_energy_pct = $6,
                contract_duration_months = $7,
                estimated_savings_pct = $8,
                offer_valid_until = $9,
                updated_at = $10
            WHERE id = $1
